{"id":305834,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/global-voices-沙特运动人士拒绝审判：我绝不容许妇女被/","date":"2013-07-27T04:15:25Z","modified":"2013-07-27T04:15:25Z","title":"Global Voices | 沙特运动人士拒绝审判：“我绝不容许妇女被贬低”","content":"<p><p>今日（5月4日），沙特<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saudi_Civil_and_Political_Rights_Association\">公民权利和政治权利协会</a>联合创始人，<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/drkhdar\">Abdulkareem al-Khudar</a>博士接受第五次开庭审判。上一次开庭时，法官仍拒绝妇女参与公审，表示她们应该留在家里。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2013/04/24/saudi-judge-bars-women-from-trial-of-human-rights-activist/\">上次审判</a>，al-Khudar博士拒绝进入法庭，理由是法庭不允许女性与男性一同参与听审。因此，法官向他发出为期四个月的逮捕令。自此之后，al-Khudr博士就一直被囚禁在Buraydah公共监狱。</p>\n<p> </p>\n</p>\n<div>上传的<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WWuHbeSLUlY\">视频</a>中，al-Khudar双手戴着手铐，离开法院大楼时，他说道：</div>\n<blockquote>\n<div>我因为试图改善这个国家的处境而被囚禁。我祈祷这一愿望能够被实现，就算牺牲我的生命也值得。</div>\n</blockquote>\n<div></div>\n<div><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-410319\" alt=\"Dr. al-Khudar, handcuffed, before the session. \" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/al-khudar-5th-session-200x300.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p>al-Khudar博士在出庭后被戴上手铐，来自 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WWuHbeSLUlY\">ACPRATube</a></p>\n</div>\n<p>法官持续拒绝妇女参与听审（其中包括al-Khudar博士的母亲和妻子）， al-khudar拒绝在庭上发言，但写了张纸条。<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s6ZjAXe6r5s\">开庭结束后</a>，他的律师读出他写的纸条，写道：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<div>我发誓我将不会容忍以伊斯兰的名义，扭曲古兰经的经文，扭曲神的意思来贬低妇女。如果这样的贬低是以法律的名义，那麽立法的人难辞其咎。</div>\n</blockquote>\n<div>下一次开庭将会在下周六5月11日举行。</div>\n<div>校对者：Ameli</div>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/osama-khalid/\" title=\"文章导读 Osama Khalid\">Osama Khalid</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/gvzhteam/\" title=\"文章导读 GV 中文化小组\">GV 中文化小组</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2013/05/04/saudi-activist-refuses-trial-i-will-not-tolerate-women-degradation/\" title=\"阅读原文  en\">阅读原文  en</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2013/07/27/12744/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br /><span><span>分享: </span> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E6%B2%99%E7%89%B9%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E6%8B%92%E7%BB%9D%E5%AE%A1%E5%88%A4%EF%BC%9A%E2%80%9C%E6%88%91%E7%BB%9D%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%B9%E8%AE%B8%E5%A6%87%E5%A5%B3%E8%A2%AB%E8%B4%AC%E4%BD%8E%E2%80%9D&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F07%2F27%2F12744%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F07%2F27%2F12744%2F&#038;desc=%E6%B2%99%E7%89%B9%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E6%8B%92%E7%BB%9D%E5%AE%A1%E5%88%A4%EF%BC%9A%E2%80%9C%E6%88%91%E7%BB%9D%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%B9%E8%AE%B8%E5%A6%87%E5%A5%B3%E8%A2%AB%E8%B4%AC%E4%BD%8E%E2%80%9D\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/\" onclick=\"javascript:var js=document.createElement (\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F07%2F27%2F12744%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F07%2F27%2F12744%2F&#038;text=%E6%B2%99%E7%89%B9%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E